ovie times, or a serie of email contacts.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"title":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}}}